data.title: VGMiu 60" Trampoline for Kids, 5 FT Indoor & Outdoor Small Toddler Trampoline with Basketball Hoop, Safety Enclosure, Baby Trampoline Toys, Birthday Gifts for Kids, Gifts for Boy and Girl, Age 1-8
about: STURDY - Rust-proof steel structure with a total of 3 U-shape legs for added stability impressive bouncing. Each U-shape foot is setting with two large suction cups, which improves stability and will not damage the floor. It will not rattle or shake when the baby jumps. It is a very humanized design. It is very simple to move from indoor to outdoor. It only takes 10 minutes to remove the protective net and steel poles, and then you can easily pass through the door.

SAFETY - Wear-resistant, UV-resistant jump pad (made of PP) can withstand high pressure and has good elasticity. Double fun with jumping and shooting actions with the built-in entertainment basketball hoop, keep your kids go to jump frequently during a day. VGMiu kids trampolines comply with ASTM F381-16 Standard Safety Specification for Components, Assembly, Use, and Labeling of Consumer Trampolines.

HEAVY LOADING - This 60" trampoline with safety enclosure for kids toddlers is safe and stable. The kids trampoline with protective net ensures your child's safety when jumping. Don't worry about getting hands or feet trapped in the gap, because they are covered by durable frame pads. (All VGMiu trampolines are fully tested for safety and durability)

APPLICATION - The newly upgraded trampoline in 2022 is the best gift for children. It is very suitable for toddler, children, baby, Your kids can have great fun and jumping exercise on VGMiu trampoline, a great way to burn off extra energy any time of the day. Can be installed indoors, outdoors, garden or backyard. Really a good gymnastics equipment for home.

PACKAGE CONTAINS - One trampoline, safety net, springs cover pad, jump pad, rust-proof steel pipe, pull tool (T-Hook), trampoline basketball hoop, 6pcs large suction cups, 10pcs pit ball, trampoline accessories and all the installation tools you need.

data.title: PlayStation 5 Digital Edition
about: Embark on an epic and heartfelt journey alongside Kratos and Atreus with the PlayStation 5 Console – God of War Ragnarök Bundle.
Bundle includes: PlayStation 5 console, DualSense Wireless Controller, Base, HDMI Cable, AC power cord, USB cable, God of War Ragnarok full game voucher
DualSense Wireless Controller integration: Feel your journey through the Norse realms, made possible by immersive haptic feedback and adaptive trigger functionality.

Stunning visuals: Bask in the beautiful worlds you travel through, brought to life by stunning art direction and arresting attention to detail. Behold enhanced reflections, lighting and shadows, as well as increased geometric detail and enhanced deformable snow.

Fully optimized for 3D Audio*: Immerse yourself in the unique soundscapes of the Nine Realms as sounds reverberate and echo throughout the environment. Use highly accurate spatial audio to hear enemies approaching from any direction, including above and below you. *3D audio with stereo headphones (analog or USB)

data.title: Battleship With Planes Strategy Board Game For Ages 7 and Up (Amazon Exclusive)
about: A twist on the classic battleship game: This battleship game features airplanes in addition to Ships for awesome strategic gameplay and epic battles
Sink Ships and crash Planes: with this edition, fans of the battleship game can crash enemy Planes in addition to sinking Ships to win
Portable Game: the battleship game includes 2 portable battle cases so players can take it with them, and Dive into an instant game on the go
A childhood favorite: remember playing the battleship game as a kid. Kids and adults can enjoy playing this entertaining game together. It's also a great strategy game. Play it in the classroom
Convenient storage: The game has convenient ship, plane, and peg storage on the side of the ocean grid
